reviewText: This movie was okay and would be worth renting, but I purchased on the recommendation of another DVD.  Watched it once and it went to my Wall Shelf Of Dead Movies.
Movie was dreadful. Cristina Kellogg is hot though. Everyone else can't act their way out of a burning building. But that ms Kellogg...

I like this film,a new face in action movies. I can tell it is an indie film but it has a lot of the big film fill. First I can tell it's shot on film... and the lead guy really know's How to fight! The cast is good and so is the action. The Locator good film...
